@startuml TourCreationAndDiscoveryFlow
title Tour Creation / Tour Discovery

skinparam swimlaneWidth same
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
skinparam activityBorderColor #2F6FED
skinparam conditionStyle diamond

|#LightBlue|Admin|
|#Lavender|System|
|#LightBlue|Customer|

|Admin|
:Step 1: Inputs tour details;

|System|
:Step 2: Validates and publishes tour;

|Admin|
:Step 3: Creates schedule;

|Admin|
:Step 4: Uploads images;

|Customer|
:Step 5: Accesses tour catalog;

|Customer|
:Step 6: Inputs search criteria;

|System|
:Step 7: Filters matching tours;

|Customer|
:Step 8: Selects tour details;

stop

@enduml